<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-25-0505 </DOCNO><TEXT>For safety and efficiency in the operation of pulverized fuel boilersit is important to know the heat transfer characteristics of the coalcombustion products. The heat transfer mechanisms, both radiation andconvective, are briefly reviewed. It is concluded that the radiativeproperties of the combustion products are poorly known while the convectiveproperties are reasonably well known. 7 refs.</TEXT></DOC>